<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head><meta charset="utf-8" /><title>Confirm account deletion</title>
<style>body,table,td{font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,"Segoe UI",Roboto,sans-serif}table{border-collapse:collapse}@media(max-width:600px){.email-container{width:100%!important}.email-content{padding:32px 20px!important}}@media(prefers-color-scheme:dark){.email-body{background-color:#09090b!important}.email-container{background-color:#18181b!important}.email-heading,.email-brand{color:#fff!important}.email-text{color:#a1a1aa!important}.email-text-muted{color:#71717a!important}.email-border{border-color:#27272a!important}}</style></head>
<body style="margin:0;padding:0;background-color:#fafafa" class="email-body"><table role="presentation" width="100%" style="background-color:#fafafa" class="email-body"><tr><td align="center" style="padding:24px 16px"><table role="presentation" width="560" class="email-container" style="background-color:#fff;border-radius:8px;max-width:560px"><tr><td class="email-content" style="padding:48px 32px"><table role="presentation" width="100%"><tr><td style="padding-bottom:16px"><span style="font-size:18px;font-weight:700;color:#09090b" class="email-brand">Better Email</span></td></tr><tr><td style="border-top:1px solid #e4e4e7;padding-bottom:24px" class="email-border"></td></tr></table><h1 style="font-size:24px;font-weight:600;color:#09090b;margin:0 0 8px 0" class="email-heading">Delete your account</h1><p style="font-size:14px;line-height:24px;color:#3f3f46;margin:0 0 12px 0" class="email-text">Hi {{user.name}},</p><p style="font-size:14px;line-height:24px;color:#3f3f46;margin:0 0 12px 0" class="email-text">We received a request to permanently delete your account. This action is irreversible.</p><table role="presentation" width="100%" style="margin:20px 0"><tr><td style="background-color:#fef2f2;border:1px solid #fecaca;border-radius:8px;padding:16px 20px"><p style="font-size:13px;line-height:20px;color:#991b1b;margin:0">All your data, including your profile, settings, and associated content, will be permanently removed and cannot be recovered.</p></td></tr></table><table role="presentation" width="100%" style="margin:24px 0"><tr><td align="center"><a href="{{url}}" style="display:inline-block;background-color:#ef4444;color:#fff;padding:14px 28px;border-radius:6px;text-decoration:none;font-size:14px;font-weight:600">Delete my account</a></td></tr></table><p style="font-size:13px;color:#71717a;margin:0" class="email-text-muted">If you did not request this, please ignore this email. Your account will remain active.</p><table role="presentation" width="100%" style="margin-top:32px"><tr><td style="border-top:1px solid #e4e4e7;padding-top:16px" class="email-border"></td></tr><tr><td style="font-size:12px;color:#71717a;padding-bottom:8px" class="email-text-muted">This link will expire in 1 hour. For security, it can only be used once.</td></tr><tr><td style="font-size:12px;color:#71717a" class="email-text-muted">Sent by Better Email</td></tr></table></td></tr></table></td></tr></table></body></html>
